snippet.title: KUNAI - Boss trailer (PC/Switch)
snippet.description:
KUNAI will be released on Nintendo Switch and PC on February 6th! 
Wishlist KUNAI on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1001800/KUNAI/

KUNAI’s adventure through its striking war-torn world emphasizes swift exploration and combat; whether it’s dancing on the heads of enemies with well-timed slashes of a katana, dodging death with grappling hook-esque kunai, or swinging over chasms to discover new areas, KUNAI equips players with an arsenal which makes experiencing every corner of its map a delight.
 
To stay current with all things KUNAI, visit the game’s official website (https://kunaigame.com/), keep tabs on The Arcade Crew on Twitter (https://twitter.com/TheArcadeCrew)
